---
description: Pytest and offline eval invariants
globs:
  - tests/**/*.py
  - evals/**/*.py
alwaysApply: false
---

# Tests

- Mock external HTTP (`requests`, Reddit, Serper) and avoid live LLM calls in CI.
- Prefer overriding `PipelineRunner` / FastAPI `get_pipeline_controller` for integration-style tests.
- `evals/` may run deterministic heuristics — keep fixtures under `evals/fixtures/`.
